aerial topdressing
Homonym Number:
Word Class:noun
Sense Number:
Definition:The spreading of fertiliser from aircraft, esp. on country inaccessible to other forms of mechanical transport; topdressing, or dusting, with fertiliser from the air.
Origin:[none]
Register:
Register 2:
Domain:[none]
Region:[none]
